{"tid":761621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(真人真事，感慨)公屋蝗孩vs 公屋蝻孩","createTime":"2018-07-30T14:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T12:00:32.000Z","uid":51200,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b2c986d14f5c51c441529db404c65cd899f16f","tid":761621,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說今日去咗個公屋屋邨做野<br />\n中午肚餓所以去咗食麥當勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隔離張枱有一個包住頭巾嘅女仔(蝻)<br />\n同兩個男仔（一個蝗一個蝻）<br />\n咁唔知點解佢哋會同一張枱啦<br />\n但係佢哋就無啦啦玩起猜包剪揼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蝻仔 ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   蝻女：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   蝗仔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蝻女/蝻仔：包剪揼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（可能為咗遷就個蝗仔所以講廣東話）<br />\n<br />\n點知<br />\n蝗仔：剪刀石頭布（普通話）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蝻女擰頭表示聽唔明<br />\n而個蝻仔可能為咗唔想落個蝗仔面，<br />\n斷斷續續咁跟住講咗句：剪刀石頭布（普通話）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後同個蝗仔猜左兩野<br />\n<br />\n突然之間，個蝻女個樣好嬲咁望住個蝻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大聲講左句：包剪揼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個蝻仔可能feel到有唔妥<br />\n即刻用返廣東話講：包剪揼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個蝗仔個樣即時西到爆炸（真係冇誇大，個樣好撚嬲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝻女蝻仔唔理佢自己圍內兩條友猜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗仔耐唔耐會叫：剪刀石頭布（普通話）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望引返兩個蝻玩<br />\n而個蝻女就會用返高兩度嘅聲線應返佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">包剪揼</span><br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後個蝗仔屈服左<br />\n講返廣東話包剪揼<br />\n三個仲玩得好開心添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n望住佢地玩，真係好感慨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時應該有幾個巴打望住，<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5f9f2191aff765d742a150ed06ebc9221224e9","tid":761621,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb7926f6a969dde10ebf1d69bbc9dfb6752cd5a1","tid":761621,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d7ddb014f1873e8cc93baf7f1246648de90cd0","tid":761621,"uid":51200,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"補充多少少<br />\n其實我唔係好肯定個蝗仔係唔係真係蝗仔<br />\n因為聽佢講廣東話係完全冇口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前去公共屋邨<br />\n最多都係聽d啊姐講廣東話講得唔正<br />\n但係OK冇問題，你最起碼會講<br />\n<br />\n今日一去真係不得了<br />\n屌你老母而家咁撚多人講普通話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由其係小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10個起碼有五個講普通話<br />\n剩返嗰五個講廣東話嘅仲係要加埋蝻先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5337d0107c3446f73855d4d969792dc7689350","tid":761621,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a744d8928da600e728e7ed5dc66ed5c8fed791ff","tid":761621,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89a93a97b7448b9e47c7a359ec634e02731a3ca0","tid":761621,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"南亞妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42e05b7810d6fe149447fc4e6dfad6c7bdf7f92","tid":761621,"uid":123820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"比個Like比小女孩"},{"pid":"c51a46bc6bf371aff80b9e9a4f79961195677508","tid":761621,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a38917925c560d6fd2a548ba247601fd0d1f33","tid":761621,"uid":83798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"而家好多小朋友講普通話啦（除左只講英文，差唔多都講普），出到街細路至中學都講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野事 我唔識分啦，當曬蝗仔算"},{"pid":"030d29572fea06e4ace9b9048d318ee64c9f46a8","tid":761621,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"焦土呀"},{"pid":"a3fa4efba2ba7a950d68008a599a56cc0867370a","tid":761621,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e0de29d97fecf7df07359289d7a06a8a2247d82","tid":761621,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"所以聽到蝗蟲話即當蝗蟲冇死,大大聲屌就得"},{"pid":"30b57c21ff629f6c928ed6a2dea93f89392446d8","tid":761621,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7a38917925c560d6fd2a548ba247601fd0d1f33","tid":761621,"uid":83798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"而家好多小朋友講普通話啦（除左只講英文，差唔多都講普），出到街細路至中學都講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野事 我唔識分啦，當曬蝗仔算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"其實都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f9f85d7b3413eca71e00379566e36e23310c32","tid":761621,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"呵呵"}]}